title: Part C
stimulusHtml:
Errors in the antidifferentiation impact the third point.

Computational errors in evaluation of the integral impact the fourth point.

The response is eligible for the fourth and fifth points with a consistent and correct use of an incorrect antiderivative based on a maximum of one error.
